GREAT game: a worthy sequel of Danganronpa 1: Trigger Happy Havoc.

And here is my comparison:
- graphic art: this second Danganronpa game is less refined then the first one;
+ gameplay: it is far better, because there are new mini-games and the old ones have been improved;
/ plot: until chapter 5, I found the plot very good but not exceptional; thanks to the last chapter (pure genius for me) the game reaches the same level of Danganronpa 1. Both are absolute Masterpieces!

My final rank: 9,6/10.

