Personally I felt more attached to the first game's characters, but this one provoked a stronger feeling of dread and despair in me. The mechanics are different, maybe even more difficult for some people, as I struggled with Logic Dives (I have potato reflexes). For me the mysteries were challenging to solve, whereas in the previous game I could more or less guess who is the culprit by gut. DR 2 is definitely different from DR 1 in several aspects, but I think both games are amazing in their own way.

